cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS 

This paper deals with local reasoning techniques for message passing concurrent programs, which is a topic that falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the use of resource usage analysis, which is relevant to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper focuses on message-passing concurrency, which is a subfield of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed systems (cs.DS).
